Package neqsim.process.examples

Class OilGasProcessSimulationOptimization.ProcessInputParameters

java.lang.Object
neqsim.process.examples.OilGasProcessSimulationOptimization.ProcessInputParameters
Enclosing class:
OilGasProcessSimulationOptimization
public static class OilGasProcessSimulationOptimization.ProcessInputParameters extends Object
Data class to hold process input parameters.

This class contains all input parameters required for running the oil and gas separation process simulation, including flow rates, temperatures, pressures, and pressure drops.

Version:
1.0
Author:
NeqSim Development Team
